<li id="cite_note-26"><b><a href="#cite_ref-26" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREF.5B.5BElaine_Pagels.5D.5D_and_.5B.5BKaren_King.5D.5D"><a href="/wiki/Elaine_Pagels" title="Elaine Pagels">Elaine Pagels</a> and <a href="/wiki/Karen_King" title="Karen King" class="mw-redirect">Karen King</a> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="2007-03-14"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="03-14"><a href="/wiki/March_14" title="March 14">March 14</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/2007" title="2007">2007</a></span>). <a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=8892042" class="external text" title="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=8892042" rel="nofollow">"The Gospel of Judas and the Shaping of Christianity"</a>. NPR<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=8892042" class="external free" title="http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=8892042" rel="nofollow">http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=8892042</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Gospel+of+Judas+and+the+Shaping+of+Christianity&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=%5B%5BElaine+Pagels%5D%5D+and+%5B%5BKaren+King%5D%5D&amp;rft.au=%5B%5BElaine+Pagels%5D%5D+and+%5B%5BKaren+King%5D%5D&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BMarch+14%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B2007%5D%5D&amp;rft.pub=NPR&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2Ftemplates%2Fstory%2Fstory.php%3FstoryId%3D8892042&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Gnostic_Gospels"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
